unnormalised: fokot ek uzkass, tumchem PAN card (zoxem, ABCDE1234F) ani bank account number (zoxem, 123456789012) fraudd tallche khatir gupt dovrat; tumcho IFSC code (zoxem, SBIN0000123) zai poddlear ghervedevarakhatir vatto zatat. Tech bhaxen, UPI IDs zoxem phone number @bankname (zoxem, 9876543210@ybl) vixim zannivkai dovrat.
normalised: Fokot ek yaad, tumcho P-A-N card, udahoronnak, A-B-C-D-E-ek-don-tin-char-F, ani bank khateacho ankdo, udahoronnak, ek-don-tin-char-ponch-so-sat-aath-nou-shunya-ek-don, dhoka talleak gupit dourat; tumcho I-F-S-C code, udahoronnak, S-B-I-N-shunya-shunya-shunya-shunya-ek-don-tin, zai tedna vyavharakhatir vanttun gheta ieta. Tech bhaxen, U-P-I I-Ds vixim chukanna ravat zoxe ki phone number @ bankachem naav, udahoronnak, nou-aath-sat-so-ponch-char-tin-don-ek-shunya @ Y-B-L.
